				<div class="entry">
                                <h2>Mortal Ghost</h2>
                                <p><em>It's a fiery hot summer, and sixteen-year-old Jesse Wright is on the run.&nbsp; An oddly gifted boy, he arrives in a new city where the direction of his life is about to change.&nbsp; He's hungry and lonely and desperate&#8212;and beset by visions of a stranger who is being brutally tortured.&nbsp; And then there are Jesse's own memories of a fire&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;.&nbsp;</em></p>

<p>Start reading or listening online from <a href="/mortal-ghost/chapter-one/">Chapter One</a>.</p>

<p><br/></p>

<div style="clear: both;"></div>

<h3>Formats</h3>

<h4>Read</h4>

<p>for free:
<a href="/mortal-ghost/chapter-one/">online</a> 
| 
<a href="/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/mortalghost-lowe.pdf">PDF</a> 
| 
Feedbooks: <a href="http://www.feedbooks.com/userbook/120">for iPhones, mobile devices, and ereaders</a> 
|
Smashwords: <a href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/58">for multiple ebook formats</a>
|
<a href="http://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/mortal-ghost-l-lee-lowe/1029199081?ean=2940000690130&amp;itm=1&amp;usri=mortal%2bghost#CustomerReviews">Barnes &amp; Noble Nook</a>
|
<a href="http://www.wattpad.com/79723-mortal-ghost">download&nbsp;to&nbsp;phone</a>
<br/>
for fee:
<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Mortal-Ghost/dp/B001VNCPJY/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1237317758&amp;sr=8-1">Amazon Kindle</a> 
|
<a href="http://www.lulu.com/content/1714151">paperback</a> with cover art by Australian artist <a href="http://lmnoonan.blogspot.com/">L.M. Noonan</a></p>

